name: Trooper Utris M'toc (V)
Lore: 'Imzig Cloud City trooper and Wing Guard leader. Attempts to protect Cloud City citizens from less reputable members of local constabulary. Never accepts a bribe.',
Text: 'Deploys free to same site as Lando or Lobot. Power +2 while defending a battle. While present at a battleground, your aliens at same and related locations are forfeit +1 (+2 if a trooper).',
